subject: Add Epics to tools
description: As a Developer, I need the option to create epic, so that I have options other than stories.

subject: Add Themes to tools
description: As a Developer, I should be able to create themes, so that I have other options

subject: Customizable Status
description: As a Developer, I should be able to change the status into anything based on the particular practice so that It can be customizable

subject: Add happiness to task
description: As a developer, I should be able to show the value of happiness in each task and add them for each task so that it can track happiness factor.

subject: Add Roles
description: As a developer, I want to assign roles

subject: Add team members
description: As a Developer, I want to add people to the project so that I know who is working on the project.

subject: Search for projects
description: As a developer, I want to view all the projects and select one so that it becomes easier to view projects.

subject: Adding bugs and issues
description: As a developer, I want bugs and issues and remove them once resolved so that i can track issues.

subject: Home Page GUI
description: As a User I should be presented with a GUI that shows all the commands so that I can choose a command to Run it.

subject: show command related menus
description: As a user I want to see the menu of a command pressed so that I can enter the related values

subject: Display Command related result page
description: As a user I want to see the result page of a command after entering the required details so that I can see the summary of the command selected.

subject: Command choices
description: As a user I want to see the list of allowed values for a command so that I can know what value to select

subject: Display Taiga API information
description: As a Developer, I should be able to view the Taiga API information from command line.
